library(pyramid)
ages <- c('0-9', '10-19', '20-29', '30-39', '40-49', '50-59', '60-')
males <- c(34,19,11,11,8,7,5)
females <- c(26,25,16,11,7,5,1)
data <- data.frame(males, females, ages)
pyramid(data)
